China has informed Russia of the water pollution situation in the country 's northeastern Songhua River , Chinese Foreign Ministry spokesman Liu Jianchao said here on Thursday .Currently , the water supply has been cut off in Harbin , capital of northeast China 's Heilongjiang Province , as the city 's water source , Songhua River , has been heavily polluted .China 's State Environmental Protection Administration ( SEPA ) said here on Wednesday that the Songhua River in northeast China suffered a major water pollution incident owing to the explosion of a petrochemical plant at the upper reaches .